Appcelerator Demo Application
=============================
This is a simple demonstration application that can quickly be leveraged to show several benefits of the Appcelerator Mobile SDK including adding elements to a view and styling the view.

## Get Started
* From Titanium or Appcelerator Studio click **File** and select **Import...**
* From the dialog box, expand the **Git** folder and select **Git Repository as New Project**
* Select the **URI** option and use this repository in the text field:  _git@github.com:appcelerator-se/DemoApp.git_
* Click **Finish**

## Key Features
* Leverages the ActionBar and Menu for Android while MobileWeb and iOS incorporate a custom Navigation Bar using device queries on XML Elemnts and in Styles
* Uses an Alloy Theme
* Showcases a basic TableView with a customized TableViewRow
* Demonstrates how to dynamically add new TableViewRows to the TableView
* All buttons are clickable, and have associated click event handlers


